cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM 

This paper deals with wireless communications and security, which are both relevant to the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) sub-categories. The use of relay nodes and the analysis of their benefits falls under the Networked Systems (cs.NI) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Finally, the paper also discusses numerical results and potential future directions, which are relevant to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
